OL,9,     Gbut the feedback leads to
OL,10,     Gquestions.
OL,11,G1615FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GIt's the final day of the
OL,13,     Gcompetition and the B&Bers meet
OL,14,     Gfor the last time. After dramatic
OL,15,     Gdiscoveries and cutting comments,
OL,16,     Gthe payments are revealed and the
OL,17,     Gwinner is announced.
